↓ Click "Mark Active" on Buster ↓

│ Pet Selector now shows: [Buster ✓] [Luna] [Charlie]     │
│ (Buster is queued in selector but view doesn't change yet)

↓ Select "Buster" from Pet Selector dropdown ↓

DASHBOARD → TRANSFORMS TO BUSTER'S DETAIL VIEW
